    {
      "para_id": "Q004866.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) The dwelling AB.IGI.BUR , the sanctuary , the mountain of snakes , where ? Inana ..., the Abzu ( whose ) god no crown ( i.e ., ruler ) would disobey , its owner , the god of Aya-ane-pada , Enki , the father who created him , made his ( = Aya-ane-pada’s ) lordship apparent ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q004866.8",
      "line_range": "8",
      "translation": "(ii 1) He ( = Aya-ane-pada ) ( then ) established the AB.IGI.BUR for him ( = Enki ) , called its name for him , and fashioned his crown for him ."
    }
  ],
